-aria-invalid use this role
-put the text "error" in front of all errors.
-should stay invalid when you tab into it
-error should show when you blur (if there is one)
-use the error list is ideal
	- make this a heading so it jumps down to it.
-dont only use color

-aria role = alert
-use aria-polite
